text: Sennar typically refers to one of two adjacent cities in the eastern Sudan near the Blue Nile. It may also refer to: * Sennar (state), Sudan * Funj Sultanate (1504-1821), also called the Kingdom of Sennar * Plain of Sennar, the lowlands along the Blue Nile west of the Ethiopian Plateau ==See also== * Sennar Dam
title: Sennar (disambiguation)
